---
title: HelloHero: Italian Pork Fusilli  with Baby Leaves & Cheddar Cheese
description: FFusilli with a cheesy tomato sauce, veggies and the combo of pork, all packed into one amazing piled-high pasta. If  that’s what you were hoping for then this dish won’t disappoint you!
